Enum BarCode.BarCodeSystem

    BarCode
    public static enum BarCode.BarCodeSystem
extends Enum<BarCode.BarCodeSystem>
    Provides bar-code system.

    Each system have one regex to help on validate data.

    See Also:
    BarCode.setSystem(BarCodeSystem), Pattern
